=======================
Virtual LAVA laboratory
=======================

Get your own LAVA laboratory up and running in no time.

Getting started
---------------

To create own laboratory, ensure that ``pip`` and ``ansible`` are installed,
then run ``bootstrap.sh``.

Prerequisites
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* pip_
* Ansible_

.. _pip: https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/installing
.. _Ansible: http://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/intro_installation.html

Running
~~~~~~~

.. code:: sh

    ./bootstrap.sh


Tested environment
------------------

========== ================
Ubuntu     16.04 ("Xenial")
VirtualBox 5.1.30
Vagrant    2.0.1
Ansible    2.4.1.0
========== ================
